name: Carpark Oulu
tagline: Sailfish app for Jolla phone which displays number of free places at parking halls in Oulu
body:
Carpark Oulu is a Sailfish application which displays reservation statuses for parking halls in Oulu. It uses [open data provided by the City of Oulu][oulu-avoin].

[oulu-avoin]: http://www.ouka.fi/oulu/oulu-tietoa/avoin-data
